OL,3,CGovernment to make #6bn welfare
OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FThe Government is planning to unveil
OL,7,Fmore than #6bn of welfare savings that
OL,8,Fwill see far tougher tests imposed for
OL,9,Fa key disability benefit, some
OL,10,Fpayments frozen in 2026, and major
OL,11,Fchanges to the way universal credit is
OL,12,Fcalculated, ITV News can reveal.
OL,14,FLiz Kendall, the work and pensions
OL,15,Fsecretary, has argued that the welfare
OL,16,Fsystem is broken and it is critical to
OL,17,Fget more people into work. But the
OL,18,Fchanges are likely to be hugely
OL,19,Fcontroversial, including with Labour
OL,20,Fbackbenchers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
