OL,6,FThe radical package of reforms will
OL,7,Fsee:
OL,9,FThe aim of the measures is to
OL,10,Fmassively increase the incentives for
OL,11,Fpeople to remain in the work-search
OL,12,Fcategory of Universal Credit, even if
OL,13,Fthey suffer with a health condition or
OL,14,Fdisability, but also to more than #6bn
OL,15,Fa year by the end of the decade.
