OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FRachel Reeves and Liz Kendall will
OL,7,Fargue that many people with
OL,8,Fdisabilities are desperate to work but
OL,9,Fsimply don't have adequate support to
OL,10,Ffind the right job, but with the move
OL,11,Fresulting in significant cuts to
OL,12,Fbenefits for some of the most
OL,13,Fvulnerable, it will be hugely
OL,14,Fcontroversial.
OL,16,FIn an interview with ITV News last
OL,17,Fmonth, the Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,18,Ftold me too many people are "taking
OL,19,Fthe mickey" by claiming benefits when
OL,20,Fthey should be working.
