OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FLiz Kendall said the number of people
OL,7,Fon benefits who pretend they can't
OL,8,Fwork is "not good enough," and "we
OL,9,Fhave to end that".
OL,11,FA survey of people on health and
OL,12,Fdisability benefits, done by the
OL,13,FDepartment for Work and Pensions,
OL,14,Frevealed that 49% of people say they
OL,15,Fcan never work. But Kendall admitted
OL,16,Fshe thinks "more of those people could
OL,17,Fwork".
