OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"I don't blame people for thinking
OL,7,Fthat they can't, because they're stuck
OL,8,Fon a waiting list for treatment, they
OL,9,Fhaven't had the proper support that
OL,10,Fthey might need from the job centre,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,FUnder these plans - even those with
OL,14,Fextreme disabilities in the unfit to
OL,15,Fwork category are likely to lose
OL,16,Fmoney. Meanwhile many will be taken
OL,17,Fout of PIP payments which are not
OL,18,Flinked to work at all- but are there
OL,19,Fto help with the additional cost of
OL,20,Fdisabilities.
