OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,FJames Taylor, Executive Director of
OL,7,Fstrategy at disability equality
OL,8,Fcharity Scope said: "Ripping PIP away
OL,9,Fwill be catastrophic for disabled
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"PIP exists because life costs more if
OL,13,Fyou are disabled. Those costs won't
OL,14,Fdisappear if the government squeezes
OL,15,Feligibility. Many disabled people use
OL,16,FPIP to get to and from work and to pay
OL,17,Ffor essential equipment like mobility
OL,18,Faids.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
