OL,3,CGovernment to make #6bn welfare
OL,4,Csavings with benefits shake-up
OL,6,F"Making it harder to get benefits will
OL,7,Fjust push even more disabled people
OL,8,Finto poverty, not into jobs.
OL,10,F"The Chancellor has a choice ` cut
OL,11,Fbenefits and increase poverty, or
OL,12,Finvest in an equal future for disabled
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,F"Making the wrong choice will have a
OL,16,Fdevastating impact on disabled people
OL,17,Fand their families."
