OL,6,FCarol Vickers, who lives in Horsforth
OL,7,Fnear Leeds and has multiple
OL,8,Fdisabilities, told me she has a full
OL,9,Ftime job, a part time job and runs a
OL,10,Fcompany, but needs PIP to help her
OL,11,Fcope with the cost of her disability.
OL,12,FShe has previously spoken to me about
OL,13,Fthe difficulty in applying for PIP and
OL,14,Fthen appealing it.
