OL,6,F"Freezing PIP next year will result in
OL,7,Fa real-terms income loss for around
OL,8,Ffour million people, 70 per cent of
OL,9,Fwhom are in low-to-middle income
OL,10,Fhouseholds. The scale of eligibility
OL,11,Frestrictions required to save #5
OL,12,Fbillion will change who the Government
OL,13,Fconsiders to be disabled. It must
OL,14,Ftread very carefully on this."
